description: Riverpod state management rules.
globs:
  - "lib/**/*.dart"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Riverpod

- Put app-wide providers in `lib/core/di/providers.dart`.
- Put feature providers in `lib/features/<feature>/presentation/providers/`.
- Keep provider state immutable where practical.
- Avoid reading providers in domain entities.
- Prefer `AsyncValue` for async UI state.
